articles.title: World War II-era tugboat returns to Central Florida birthplace - WKMG News 6 & ClickOrlando
articles.description: A historic tugboat built in DeLand in 1944 has made its final voyage back into Volusia County after being in Europe for 79 years.
articles.content:
VOLUSIA COUNTY, Fla. A historic tugboat built in DeLand in 1944 has made its final voyage back into Volusia County after being in Europe for 79 years.
